  <brief_title>Trial for the Treatment of Newly Diagnosed Mature B-Cell Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia (B-ALL), Burkitt's Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma (NHL) and Other High-grade Lymphoma in Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter Study to Optimise Therapy of B-ALL, Burkitt's NHL and High-Grade Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma in Adults (Amend 7)</official_title>
